---
title: Spring Lemon, Leek and Pea Linguine with Cheese and Rocket
description: Spring has sprung! A new season of veg is ready for our plates, which is why we've created this Spring Lemon, Leek and Pea Linguine. Making the most of fresh peas and sweet leeks, this primavera pasta is sure to put a spring in your step.
